title: Did he destroy the Kenosha Correctional Building in the protests?
subtitle: Activist Sean King participated in a video of smoke escalating from what he said was "totally burned" in the correctional department.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: :: During the protests following the shooting by the police of Jacob Blake in Kenosha, Wisconsin, the Kinusha facility run by the State Department of Corrections was set on fire and completely destroyed.
